Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在市政大楼后的垃圾箱里发现了无线电零件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I found the radio parts in a dumpster behind the municipal building.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从安全角度来说  这些东西绝不会被丢在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'd never be left there for security reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以某人肯定把它当成了垃圾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so someone clearly thought it was trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它不是垃圾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it wasn't trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只是需要一点呵护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It just needed some love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我印象最深的是一家冰淇淋店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have the most vivid memory of an ice-cream shop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里拥有最美味的黑树莓冰淇淋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the most marvelous batch of black raspberry ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内幕冰淇淋店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Inside Scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常去那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I used to go there all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说不定在同一天去过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hell, we might've been there on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此  你就必须回答一个重要问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, knowin' this, there's a critical question needs answerin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.93,0:00:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢蛋筒还是华夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cake cone or waffle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是这样开始聊天的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's how we started talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:01:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们什么都聊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we talked about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈天说地  漫无边际\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything and nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不住相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just can't help but believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是上天注定让我们见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that this is a celestially ordained meet-and-greet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没有泄露过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No bean-spillage here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但尤金  我的同伴超级谨慎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, Eugene, my people are uber cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们离得很近...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if we're close...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想过离开这地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never thought about leaving this place before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我想过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I-I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从不相信这有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I never let myself believe it was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮  事实是我非常想见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Truth is, Stephanie, I'd just very much like to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但后来我哥哥介入了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But then my brother got involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很不高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and he was not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这不是你想的那样  -是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It's not what you think. - Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我今天做了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wanna know what I did today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我调查了一起严重通信违规事件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I investigated a massive communications breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然某人在用未授权的电台\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently, someone on an unauthorized radio station
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与墙外的非正规社区通话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has been talking to a rogue community outside of our walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩斯比在严查这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, then. Hornsby's all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我  这不是你干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me it wasn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你告诉我  你不会偷偷跑出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please tell me that you were not about to sneak out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去火车场见一个陌生人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to meet some stranger at a rail yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能怎么说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What could I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克斯  这很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Max, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对联邦的所有人来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For everyone at the Commonwealth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是对我和你来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but especially for me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好祈祷霍恩斯比没认出你的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You better pray Hornsby doesn't realize that was your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我越线了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I knew I'd crossed a line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有霍恩斯比盯着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And with Hornsby on the prowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去见你是不可能了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}getting out to see you was impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你和另一个自称是史蒂芬妮的女人出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then you turn up with some other girl calling herself Stephanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她冒用着我的话  -多撒点彩糖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Using my words... - Extra sprinkles, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:02:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不会是坚果巧克力口味吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That wouldn't happen to be Rocky Road there, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来很幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You seemed so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我没有声张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, I kept my head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道还能怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't know what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  麦克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, Max. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还需要什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I get you anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰淇淋  茶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ice cream? Tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我那混蛋儿子消停一天吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A day without my son acting like a little asshole?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我给你拿冰淇淋吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll get you that ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, and, Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让银行取消塞巴斯蒂安的信用额度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have the bank cut off Sebastian's line of credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这能让他安分点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe that'll whip him into shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后霍恩斯比来见了帕梅拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then Hornsby came to see Pamela...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}通信里那个人  他终于承认了...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That guy from the comms breach? Finally admitted...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他嚷嚷着你和亚历山大的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and he was buzzing about you and Alexandria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我一直没有...  -他在谋划什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I never - What's he planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他野心勃勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能没事  只是重建\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could mean nothing -- just the rebuild.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿橙盔甲的讨厌我的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The big guy in the orange armor who hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你哥哥吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  但是  尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, but, Eugene --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是史蒂芬妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're Stephanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我是麦克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. I'm Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么史蒂芬妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no Stephanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那其实是我妈妈的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it was my mother's name, really --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-对不起  -所以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I-I-I'm sorry. - So --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里离家很远  兰斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a long way from home, Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些社区非常适合我们的设想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But these communities are perfect for what we're envisioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的设想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What you'reenvisioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为我们需要这样动用资源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not convinced we need to stretch our resources like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顾实力地扩张帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grow your empire further than your power can extend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会失去帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and lose your empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得没那么戏剧化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think it's quite that dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你什么叫戏剧化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, how's this for dramatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这次不顺利  我们就退出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If this doesn't go well, we're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人要么自愿永久加入我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These people are free to stay with us permanently
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么回去自己修家园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or they can go home and finish their own repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里要做的事已经够多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's enough to do at home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无暇去操心另一个州的几个小社区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}without having to worry about a couple of small communities in another state.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给个机会吧  帕梅拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Give it a chance, Pamela.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真认为你会惊喜的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I really think you might be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快搞好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's wrap it up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey. Leave it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遮住窗户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, cover that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦  我是帕梅拉·弥尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aaron. Pamela Milton.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想参观一下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, care for the grand tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-正合我意  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I would expect nothing less. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大是个自给自足的生态社区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, Alexandria was a self-sustaining ecological community.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有饮用水  太阳能板  农作物种植系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have water, solar panels, and, uh, a crop system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁设计的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who is the engineer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不记得有这个人  - 其实没这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I don't recall anyone from intake. - Uh, no one, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划是一个联盟社区的领袖给我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We got the plans from the leader of an allied community.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛姬·李\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maggie Rhee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的人研究了设计图  建了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, some of our people studied the blueprints, and we built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么偏僻的地方  你怎么保证安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you keep a place like this safe with it being so isolated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打过很多场仗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fought a lot of fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是这里的领袖之一吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were one of the leaders here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我猜可以这样说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, yeah, I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We all were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾变前你做什么工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What'd you do before all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少对我们来说不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Least, not to us, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和我记忆中一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She looks just how I remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What, you knew her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去在慈善圈  我们常有交集\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, we used to cross paths quite a bit in philanthropy circles back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当时我对政治不感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I had no interest in politics at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她生来善于掌权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She, however, was born to run things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个什么样的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was she like as a leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她接纳了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She brought us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之前从没有遇到过她那样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'd never met anybody like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你钦佩她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You admire her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  非常钦佩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. Very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为我们建立了这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, she built all this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这值得我们为之奋斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something worth fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这里陷落了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  但我们总能重建\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, but we always brought it right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里陷落过不止一次吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It fell more than once?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  -有行尸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yeah. - We've got a breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在这里  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay here, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪安娜是怎么死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did you lose Deanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被咬了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She was bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她转变了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did she turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不得不杀了她  是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had to put her down. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我在这里看够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I've seen enough here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  以西结  杰瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Morning, Ezekiel. Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也早上好  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And a good morning to you, too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mm. Okay, let's get into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当天早上只能喝水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So nothing but water morning of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能吃固体食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No food. No solids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要你空腹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need you on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生  我们只是来做例行检查的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doc, we're just here for a routine check-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被告知这是术前血检\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was told this is pre-op blood work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保他病情稳定  能做手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To make sure he's stable enough for the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摘除肿瘤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To take out this tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人告诉过你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did no one tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我还在排队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought I was still on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你排在最前面了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, now you're at the top of that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很走运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人要等好几年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some people wait years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,费用怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about his bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,付清了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's paid up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是怎么排上的  我都很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, however it came to pass, I'm thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会照顾好你的  以西结\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're going to take good care of you, Ezekiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周五九点见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See you Friday at nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is so frickin' awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wha-- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  老大  这是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, come on, boss, this is good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是巧合  可能是搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe it's a coincidence. Maybe it's a clerical error.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是老天有眼  不管怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe it's divine intervention. Either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得你总该转运了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}don't you think you deserve a little luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕梅拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pamela.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕梅拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pamela.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞秋准备好见你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rachel's ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真有福  门口就有这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're blessed to have this at your door step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了海边旅馆的建立过程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I heard how Oceanside came to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们与救世军和低语者的战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}About your battles with the Saviors and the Whisperers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这证明了你们社区很有实力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Says a lot about strength of your community.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴你们能成为联邦的合作伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm excited to have you as partners of the Commonwealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦说你们想在协议里加上贸易条款\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aaron mentioned there was a trade provision that you'd like worked into our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和山顶寨的领袖玛姬·李谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We spoke to Maggie Rhee. The leader of Hilltop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说她没有和你们合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She told us she's not partnered with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们向山顶寨提出了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We offered Hilltop the same agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与亚历山大一样的协议  但玛姬拒绝了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as with Alexandria, but Maggie declined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大有过自己的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alexandria's gone its own way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但山顶寨和玛姬一直支持着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Hilltop and Maggie have always been there for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们续签了互相保卫条约  我要遵守它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We renewed our mutual protection pact, and I'm gonna honor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果玛姬决定与你们合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If Maggie decides to partner with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也会合作  出于对她的尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we will, too, out of respect for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话  海边旅馆将拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Otherwise, Oceanside's a "No."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问一句  如果你不能在搞砸前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Question -- what was the point of bringing you along
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我有用的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you can't give me any helpful intel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还带着你来做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in advance of shit blowing up in our faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修缮亚历山大的是你们的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your people have been fixing up Alexandria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行尸进来又不是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not my fault the walker got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞秋和山顶寨的事你应该知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You should've known about Rachel and Hilltop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我会读心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I'm a mind-reader?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得帕梅拉会怎么看这次绕道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you think this little detour looks to Pamela?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像我们没准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It looks like we're not prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像你没准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It looks like you're not prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰斯  你了解帕梅拉  我不了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lance, you know Pamela, alright? I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没料到这种事  不是我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You didn't anticipate this? It's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再假装你比我更在乎亚历山大了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop acting like Alexandria means more to you than it does to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  我们的目标一致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right now, you and I want the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我们在同一条沉船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which means you and I are in the same sinking boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛姬会给我们添麻烦吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is Maggie gonna make this difficult for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Huh. Fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对帕梅拉来说  非黑即白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is all or nothing for Pamela.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果玛姬拒绝  海边旅馆退出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So if Maggie says no and Oceanside walks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大也会被断供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alexandria is cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们会自己想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then we'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在我们介入前  你们好得很呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'Cause it was going so well before we stepped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定是玛姬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must be Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经吃过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I already ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我放在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll just leave it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's good to see you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛姬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maggie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么信任这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you trust these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说我们信任了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who says we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我何时信任过任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When do I ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到亚历山大被清理了倒是挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's good to see Alexandria getting cleaned up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少他们说话算话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Least their word meant something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  有五万人住在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, there's like 50,000 people living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少49.9%都看起来是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least 49.9 seem like decent enough folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这不是永久的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it's not forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定不和我们一起走吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You sure you don't want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用独自打拼的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't have to do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前锋部队发现了尸群\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The forward unit picked up a swarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有一些多余的枪支\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have some extra rifles with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在他们处理尸群时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So while they're handling that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥尔顿总管提议我们一起去打猎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Governor Milton proposed that we all go hunting,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you're up for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动静这么大  会把食物都吓跑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll scare all the food away stomping around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和玛姬一队  你们自己搭伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll go with Maggie, and you boys pair off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我不需要护卫了  将军\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't need a minder this time, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情怎么会变得这么糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did things get so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁又知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do they ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过很多社区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've met so many communities,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然不明白为什么一些社区足够幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I still can't figure out what makes some lucky and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能抵挡住这个世界  而另一些社区不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}able to fight off the world while others can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信运气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't believe in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉你有意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sensing more of an opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运气就是机遇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, luck is about opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认识比你机遇更多的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know anybody who's had more opportunity than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要实话实说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, since we're being honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摊开了说  玛姬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cards on the table, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这次并不想来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't want to come on this tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我管理着成千上万人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have thousands of people under my care
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种责任让我夜不能寐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that responsibility keeps me up at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是当领袖的代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's the price of leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都有代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything costs something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说  代价是睡眠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For me, it's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我凌晨三点在想什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know what I think about at 3:00 A.M.?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能信任谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who can we trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们如何保障安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do we stay safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照我们的标准  你们都是小社区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your communities are small by our standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不确定与你们往来是否值得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wasn't sure the risk of going back and forth would be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么还来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确的盟友能让我们更强大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The right allies make us stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界属于我们  而不是死人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This world belongs to us, not the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你们几位  听到你们的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meeting all of you, hearing all your stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证实了我一直坚信的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has confirmed what I've always believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事物有一种自然秩序  如今已经消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is a natural order to things that has vanished,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种秩序应该被重建\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that order needs to be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这能为我们的孩子提供一个未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It provides a future for our kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1500万个城邦国家为了权力和资源互相争斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}15 million little city-states fighting each other for power and resources
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不可能提供那种稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is never going to be able to provide that kind of stability.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你们提供的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm offering you the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们与海边旅馆的互相保卫条约一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}your mutual protection pact with Oceanside did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个能保护你们的势力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone who has your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just thought I'd see how you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做饭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um, cooking, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你饿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜比拉和杰瑞给我留了点便餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nabila and Jerry left me a buffet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好  -比较酥脆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Okay. - It's, um, crispy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰瑞说你今天去检查了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jerry said you had a check-up today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么进展吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anything come up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a funny thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:20:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么了  -托米说我被安排动手术了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - Tomi said I was scheduled for surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把我排到了前面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They bumped me up in the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's great. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是吧  -等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Right? - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的债务被抹去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My debt was wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩斯比欠我一个人情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hornsby owed me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是作弊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想让你死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I don't want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡萝尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Carol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排队都是骗人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those lines are a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得帕梅拉·弥尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think Pamela Milton would think twice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为她那混账儿子做这种事会迟疑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before doing the same thing for her shitty son?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进过医院吗  卡萝尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you been inside that hospital, Carol?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你进过  你就会看到那些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'Cause if you had been, you'd see all those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受着苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着接受治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Waiting for treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为制度有问题  你就应该死吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're supposed to just die because the system is broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲的人心安理得地得到了更多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lesser men have been given more and done nothing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是差劲的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are not a lesser man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那叫独裁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think that's called an autocracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由并没有消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Liberties haven't gone anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是山顶寨的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're the leader at Hilltop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你负责做决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You make the decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为你是独裁者吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You consider yourself an autocrat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按照迪安娜和乔吉教我的方式领导社区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I-I lead the way I was taught by Deanna and Georgie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们建立的社区很公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The communities that we built are fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦也很公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Commonwealth is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你比其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, but you drive a nicer car
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开更好的车  住更好的房子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and live in a nicer house than everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比普通工人的责任更大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have more responsibilities than the average worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领袖必须让人们向往\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A leader has to give her people something to look up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我希望人们向往我做成的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alright, well, I want people to look up to what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做的事  而不是我的特权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and what I do, not what I have that they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.44,0:22:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来  还是我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want it or shall I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想对付你身后那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I was thinking about going after the one behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm great. How are you?
