Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.81,0:29:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,披萨  冰淇淋  应有尽有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pizza, ice cream. The works.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.27,0:29:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.98,0:29:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要菠萝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No pineapple.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.48,0:29:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是认真的  杰瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm serious, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.73,0:29:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,披萨上放菠萝太荒唐了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pineapple on pizza makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.23,0:29:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,披萨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.52,0:29:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这段时间只能吃流食了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not eating anything but Jell-O for a while, hotshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.14,0:29:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张到手抖吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nervous twitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.10,0:30:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运币\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lucky coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.98,0:30:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前有一只幸运兔脚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had a lucky rabbit's foot once.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.98,0:30:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的狗连着兔子一起叼回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My dog brought it home with the rabbit still attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.52,0:30:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我父亲给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My old man gave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.60,0:30:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候以为这是纯金的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I was a kid, I thought it was made of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.39,0:30:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果只是镀金的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Turns out, it's just gold-plated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.19,0:30:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面不过是镍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Inside's same as a lowly nickel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.85,0:30:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你决定了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you decided yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.39,0:30:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能从中得到什么好处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you get out of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.27,0:30:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  玛姬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.27,0:30:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别假装看不到眼前的现实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's not pretend the obvious isn't staring us in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.73,0:30:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你力不从心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're in over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.19,0:30:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是很了解我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't know me very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.35,0:30:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很聪明  听得出什么是好提议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you're smart enough to know a good offer when you hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.60,0:30:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我也很聪明  知道我刚惹怒了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'm smart enough to know I've just pissed you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.27,0:31:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没有回答我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't answered my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.35,0:31:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alright. I'll bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.02,0:31:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次去亚历山大时  我能看出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The first time I went to Alexandria, I could see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.60,0:31:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的潜力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.23,0:31:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛姬  你真的认为现在的山顶寨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maggie, do you really believe that Hilltop, as it currently stands,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.06,0:31:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你能拥有的最好的东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is the best you'll ever have?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.69,0:31:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是亚历山大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or Alexandria?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.64,0:31:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至是海边旅馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or even Oceanside?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看周围\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.06,0:31:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能拥有更多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can have so much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.10,0:31:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.27,0:31:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从联邦的音乐会接赫谢尔回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}being able to pick Hershel up from a concert at the Commonwealth,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.44,0:31:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带他去亚历山大看医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}take him to a doctor's appointment in Alexandria,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.31,0:31:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在海边旅馆乘船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then jump on a boat at Oceanside,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.52,0:31:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿着海岸航行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}traveling up the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.31,0:31:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海岸上会有什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And what's up that coast?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.73,0:31:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个港口城市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Another port town?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.56,0:31:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一所学校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Another school?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.02,0:31:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一所大学怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How about a university?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.94,0:32:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有想象过送儿子去大学上大一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you ever imagined being able to drop your son off for his freshman year of college?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.98,0:32:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾试图建过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tried to build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.98,0:32:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.39,0:32:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们的看法一致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because you and I see things the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.81,0:32:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象一下你想建立的那个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Imagine the world you want to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.10,0:32:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住这个想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold it in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.89,0:32:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想象一下五万个联邦工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now picture the power of 50,000 Commonwealth workers
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.19,0:32:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你实现这个设想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}helping you make that vision a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.10,0:32:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想到了那时  你能做到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Think what you could accomplish then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.89,0:32:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸群来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Swarm incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.94,0:32:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.52,0:33:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.35,0:34:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象一下每次警报响起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Imagine not having to deal with this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.98,0:34:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不用应付行尸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}every time that alarm goes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.77,0:34:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  我们可以一直建设\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, we could keep building.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.69,0:34:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再建建停停了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No more starts and stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.39,0:34:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道有很多要考虑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know there's a lot to consider,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.64,0:34:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看看周围\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but, I mean, look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.60,0:34:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.19,0:34:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.02,0:34:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.60,0:34:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.56,0:34:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克森  入列\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dixon. Fall in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.02,0:34:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.06,0:35:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住  他们一直在看着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remember, they're always watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.35,0:35:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Got me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.52,0:35:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.31,0:35:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向左转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Left face.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.48,0:35:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齐步走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forward march.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.31,0:35:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里从不无聊  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never a dull moment here, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.98,0:35:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We try.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.23,0:35:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.44,0:35:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没人受伤  四肢完好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, no injuries, all limbs intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.44,0:35:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这算个好日子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd call that a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.94,0:35:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但山顶寨不会接受你的提议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But the Hilltop's gonna pass on your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.56,0:35:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能问原因吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.89,0:35:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为就像你说的  一切都有代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'Cause, like you said, everything costs something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.44,0:36:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  请别关门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, please don't shut the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.31,0:36:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在类似内幕冰淇淋的店里找到了美味树莓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Found some raspberry goodness of the Inside Scoop variety.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.56,0:36:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是黑树莓  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not exactly black raspberry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.10,0:36:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  很冰的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}please, it's very cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.64,0:37:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  麦克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um, I'm so sorry, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.60,0:37:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不绅士的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For my ungentleman-like behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.06,0:37:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃避和不听你说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For running away. For not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.89,0:37:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时伤心而困惑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was bruised and confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.60,0:37:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你当时很无礼  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You were pretty damn rude. - I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.19,0:37:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.64,0:37:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让霍恩斯比操控了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I let Hornsby get inside my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.27,0:37:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一场史无前例的心理入侵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and it was an infiltration of the most epic proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.73,0:37:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是条毒蛇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He is a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.39,0:37:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更像条虫子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More like a worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.60,0:37:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让一个冒牌货进入了我的心房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I let an imposter into my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.48,0:37:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我的家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.85,0:37:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我让她读了我的手稿  -手稿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I let her read my manuscript. - Manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.19,0:37:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.19,0:37:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在写一本小说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm writing a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.94,0:37:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有墓室吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Was a sepulcher involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.31,0:37:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.77,0:37:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是发生在喀尔巴阡山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did it take place in the Carpathian Mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.27,0:37:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喀尔巴阡山  对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Carpathian Mountains, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.60,0:37:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然让她读了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You let her read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.81,0:37:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为她是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought she was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.73,0:37:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  但是  尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, but, Eugene...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.56,0:37:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.27,0:37:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在一起那么久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After all that time we spent together,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.06,0:37:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉了彼此那么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}everything we told each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.73,0:38:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎会不知道她不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how could you not know it wasn't me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.73,0:38:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do-- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.85,0:38:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜很早以前  我就发现了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I guess I figured out a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.98,0:38:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和大部分人不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I'm not like most folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.44,0:38:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很早就习惯了被拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got used to rejection PDQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.27,0:38:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时我甚至都没意识到那是拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Didn't even realize it was rejection some of the times,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.27,0:38:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可以说  这种事经常发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but, well, suffice it to say, it happened a fair amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.89,0:38:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我总是怀疑我们的感情只是幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So there was a part of me that always wondered if our connection was all in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.44,0:38:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我来了这里后  她没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But when I got here, and she didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.64,0:38:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我推开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}push me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.39,0:38:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迫切希望这份感情是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just so badly wanted this to be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.06,0:38:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以至于有时忽略了微小的线索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And subtle cues escape me sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.77,0:38:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我从没想过要伤害你  麦克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anyway, I never meant to hurt you, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.52,0:38:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的意图不能成为后果的借口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But my intent does not excuse my impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.89,0:38:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如何才能补偿你  你允许我试试吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How can I make this up to you? Will you allow me to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.94,0:39:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.39,0:39:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能读你的小说吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I read your novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.27,0:39:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来不幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, as ill fortune would have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.31,0:39:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来见我时  我正在烧唯一的实体版\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you came upon me whilst I was burning the only physical copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.10,0:39:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  大部分内容我已经记住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, I have committed much of the text to memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.35,0:39:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,概念是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was the concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.14,0:39:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个叫史蒂芬·波特曼的侦探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A gumshoe by the name of Steph Portman
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.02,0:39:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被卷入了轰轰烈烈的国际劫案中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is caught up in a rollicking international caper,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.52,0:39:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他试图避免核灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}trying to avert nuclear disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.23,0:39:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并应对国内错综复杂的法律官僚体系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and navigate the intricacies of the legal bureaucracies back at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.98,0:39:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没把地方检察官写成贪官吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You didn't make the District Attorney corrupt, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.60,0:39:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.14,0:39:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种老套没人会惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That would've surprised exactly no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.06,0:40:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我给他了一个恶毒的孪生兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did, however, give him an unsavory twin brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.69,0:40:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶的孪生兄弟  不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Evil twin. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.94,0:40:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这样觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.89,0:40:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该把那个孪生兄弟写成科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You should, um, make the twin a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.02,0:40:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加大核威胁的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ramp up the stakes on the nuclear threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.81,0:40:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是这样写的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is exactly what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.89,0:40:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.77,0:40:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就像过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just...felt like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.39,0:40:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有样东西要给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here. I got something for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.85,0:40:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱迪思给的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's from Judith.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.56,0:40:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说以防你再逼赫谢尔吃马肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She said in case you're making Hershel eat more horse meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.89,0:40:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.35,0:40:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.44,0:40:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.73,0:40:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.64,0:40:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你需要我  你知道去哪找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you need me, you know where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.44,0:40:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Same for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.39,0:41:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.56,0:41:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走了  玛姬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm leaving, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.39,0:41:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人要跟我一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some of the others are coming with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.64,0:41:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you should, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.31,0:41:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得小心该信任谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You need to be careful who you trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.44,0:41:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比任何人都懂这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know that better than anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.23,0:41:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也得知道何时该求助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You also have to know when to ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.56,0:41:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在比以往更困难  不必如此的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's harder than it has ever been, and it doesn't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.02,0:41:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常敬重你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I respect the hell outta you,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.52,0:41:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我撑不住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.85,0:41:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.10,0:41:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一次值得肯定的努力  兰斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was a worthy effort, Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.56,0:41:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.89,0:41:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.02,0:42:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's time to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.64,0:42:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有亚历山大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We still have Alexandria.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.10,0:42:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是需要时间说服剩下两个社区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just need time to get the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.10,0:42:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次试图纳入三个新社区很大胆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was a bold move, trying to bring three new communities into the fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.27,0:42:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解这种事为何会吸引你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I get why something like that would be appealing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.10,0:42:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟得有人管它们  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone needs to run them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.19,0:42:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人选将由你决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That selection would be at your discretion,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.27,0:42:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显而易见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.35,0:42:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显而易见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.31,0:42:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会假装你做这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna pretend that you were doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.11,0:42:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了联邦  而不是为了你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for the good of the Commonwealth rather than for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.81,0:42:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是为了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.23,0:42:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我们认识以来  你一直野心勃勃  兰斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've been ambitious our whole lives, Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.81,0:42:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野心向来难以收敛  所以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ambition is notoriously hard to reel in. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.52,0:42:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想试着做成这事  当然可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you want to try and make it work, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.06,0:42:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你懈怠了家里的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if your job at home starts to suffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.06,0:42:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会有后果的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there will be consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.77,0:42:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦永远摆在第一位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Commonwealth always comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.98,0:43:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.06,0:43:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰斯  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lance, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.89,0:43:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"A" Plus.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.60,0:43:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是怎么说亚历山大的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What'd she say about Alexandria?
